Two measures of [[Sergei Vasilievich Rachmaninoff|Sergei Rachmaninoff]]'s [[Prelude in C-sharp minor (Rachmaninoff)|Prelude in C{{music|sharp}} minor]] showing dynamic markings {{serif|'''''sffff'''''}}. The top two staves are both played by the right hand, the bottom two by the left.
